  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (5 Days) #76321",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: HVAC Solutions Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistance</strong></li><li>Working Location: Mac Pherson (near MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days. Mon – Fri (8.30am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, unload, and verify incoming goods, ensuring items match purchase orders.</li><li>Store materials and products systematically in assigned areas, keeping stock organized.</li><li>Pick and pack product securely with correct labelling and required documentation.</li><li>Take part in stocktakes and inventory audits, keeping records up to date.</li><li>Reporting any inventory shortage or overages to supervisors.</li><li>Handle warehouse equipment—such as forklifts, pallet jacks, or reach trucks for safe loading and unloading of goods.</li><li>Prepare shipments for dispatch, completing necessary documents and coordinating with logistics providers for timely deliveries.</li><li>Maintain a clean and safe warehouse environment, follow health and safety procedures.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum ITE certification.</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant warehouse experience.</li><li>Basic understanding of inventory control and warehouse procedures.</li><li>Valid Singapore forklift license is required.</li><li>Able to carry goods up to 20kg when necessary.</li><li>Good skill in Microsoft Excel is an added advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76321 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
